rt, intuitive decisions. Combining decisive action with emotional conviction, future-facing firms seize the day. Fast/Forward paints the big picture of a new approach to strategy and provides the necessary playbook to make your company fit for the future.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 0aDecision making. 0aIndustrial management. 0aStrategic planning. 0aSuccess in business. 4aachievement. 4aadhocracy. 4aambidextrous. 4abig data. 4abureaucracy. 4aexperimentation. 4ameritocracy. 4aopportunity-focused coordination. 4aparadoxes of progress. 4apurpose. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Strategic Planning.2bisacsh1 aRidderstråle, Jonas, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311070369640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150360231140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503602311423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781503602311.jpg  a978-3-11-070369-6  SUP Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles